How long for my ad to get approved?

On average, we review ads within 4 hours on weekdays, and up to 8 hours on weekends. If your account is new and not yet verified, the process might take a bit longer. For more details, you can check out our FAQ here: [Ad Approval Time](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad).
Great! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
